ralph george macchio , jr. ( , ; born november 4 , 1961 ) is an american actor , best known for his roles as daniel larusso in the karate kid series , eugene martone in crossroads , bill gambini in my cousin vinny , and johnny cade in the outsiders .

martial artists : " rocky " director john g. avildsen directed this 1984 ralph macchio film & 2 of its sequels

